{"title":"CentOS 6 GCC 编译升级至5.1.0","uid":"41c7b401621718ddd84559c090fb4c3e","slug":"CentOS 6 GCC 编译升级至5.1.0","date":"2021-01-07T05:14:50.000Z","updated":"2025-04-30T08:11:18.832Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/CentOS 6 GCC 编译升级至5.1.0.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>由于 CentOS 6 停止更新支持了, 官方都将yum软件源关闭了. 原来的安装方式已失效. 只能手动编译了.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>下载GCC 5.1.0 源码包: <code>wget http://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/gnu/gcc/gcc-5.1.0/gcc-5.1.0.tar.bz2</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>解压: <code>tar xvf gcc-5.1.0.tar.bz2</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>安装gcc需要下载诸如gmp、mpfr、mpc等依赖文件，执行<code>download_prerequisites</code>将会自动下载这些软件并解压到当前目录: <code>./contrib/download_prerequisites</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>新建一个build目录, 执行mark前的configura</p>\n <figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkdir build</span><br><span class=\"line\">cd build </span><br><span class=\"line\">../configure --prefix=/usr/local/gcc-5.1.0 --disable-multilib --enable-languages=c,c++,java</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li><p>开始编译: <code>make -j4</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>安装 </p>\n <figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">make install</span><br><span class=\"line\">which gcc # 将原来的gcc改名</span><br><span class=\"line\">mv /usr/bin/gcc /usr/bin/gcc_bak</span><br><span class=\"line\">ln  -s /usr/local/gcc-5.1.0/bin/x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu-gcc-5.1.0 /usr/bin/gcc # 创建软连接</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ol>\n<p>测试: <code>gcc --version</code></p>\n","text":"由于 CentOS 6 停止更新支持了, 官方都将yum软件源关闭了. 原来的安装方式已失效. 只能手动编译了. 下载GCC 5.1.0 源码包: wget h...","permalink":"/post/CentOS 6 GCC 编译升级至5.1.0","